[
    {
        "source_sentence": "師子莊嚴王菩薩請問經",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大唐中印度三藏那提譯",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是我聞：一時佛在王舍城耆闍崛山中，與",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大比丘眾千二百五十人俱，菩薩摩訶薩五百人，天、龍、夜叉、乾闥婆、阿修羅、迦樓羅、緊那羅、摩睺羅伽、人非人等，無量八部前後圍遶聽佛說法。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時眾中有菩薩摩訶薩，名師子莊嚴王，從座而起來詣佛所，頂禮雙足遶無數匝，而白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我於過去億百千那由他諸佛所廣預大會，然未曾覩如今所見。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲有請問，唯願聽許。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「隨汝所問，當為解說。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b23_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時師子莊嚴王菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來往昔修何勝行，今獲如是人天中尊，為諸菩薩大聲聞眾天龍八部之所圍遶，供養恭敬尊重讚歎？",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願為演說往昔因緣，令諸眾生獲大善利。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告師子莊嚴王菩薩摩訶薩言：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今乃能安樂眾生故作是問。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697b29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽諦聽！",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當為汝說。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我憶過去無量世時，有佛出興，名不可思議光明如來、應供、正遍知、明行足、善逝、世間解、無上士、調御丈夫、天人師、佛、世尊。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有長者名曰上施，自恃豪富不信正法，而於佛所無歸敬心。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一比丘名毘闍耶三皤蒱我反婆，見是長者生憐愍心，起大方便，要令此人發心修行得成正覺。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念已，往長者家。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時上施覩見比丘，顏貌殊勝威德備足，諸根寂定容光熾盛，肅然敬重即起奉迎。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頂禮既訖設座令坐，合掌白言：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『自顧薄德，忽蒙臨降。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「爾時比丘告長者曰：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c12_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『有大法門，名八曼茶羅，功德無量。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今為汝說，廣欲慧利諸天人故。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c13_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有眾生聞此法門能修行者，在所生處獲四勝報：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、與善知識諸大菩薩同處受生，有大眷屬，資財豐足；",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、眷屬既多自在無礙；",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、身相圓備無有疾病；",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、眾具自然隨念而至，縱被山壓身無痛苦，能知眾生心之所念，慈悲憐愍將護拯濟。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「爾時上施聞是法已，歡喜踊躍重加頂禮，讚言：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願為廣說八曼茶羅最勝法門，我當修學。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「比丘告曰：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝欲知此最勝法者，先發是願：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我欲供養三世諸佛、大菩薩眾、聲聞、緣覺。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c23_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是語已，道場之處當作方壇，名曼茶羅。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "廣狹隨時，其最小者縱廣四指、或一搩手，用種種香及以餘物，或地上作。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "方院之內列八圓場，為欲供養八菩薩故。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為八？",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0697c27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀世音菩薩、彌勒菩薩、虛空藏菩薩、普賢菩薩、執金剛主菩薩、文殊師利菩薩、止諸障菩薩、地藏菩薩。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，長者！",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此八曼茶羅最勝法門，是彼不可思議光明如來所說，我親受持，今為汝說，應當修學廣令流布；",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a03_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "用此善根，迴向阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『長者當知，若有修行此八法者，則為供養三世諸佛、大菩薩眾、緣覺、聲聞；",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "斯人常為諸天擁護。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a06_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸國王能自修學、若使人作，使王國內諸惡皆滅。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸善男子及善女人，有能修學八法門者，命終之後不墮惡趣、邊地、邪見、不善律儀、貧窮家生。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故當知，欲得現在未來勝上報者，當學如上八種法門；",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲得受身端正聰明利智，若欲上生四天王處，亦應修學八曼茶羅。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是欲生三十三天、夜摩天、兜率陀天、化樂天、他化自在天，乃至帝釋、梵王、魔王、轉輪聖王所生處者，皆當修學如上八法。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲得天上人中大姓家生，眷屬成就財寶盈溢，身心安樂名稱遠聞，所出教命無不信受，於諸眾中最尊最勝，皆應修學如上八法。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲修成須陀洹果、斯陀含果、阿那含果、阿羅漢果、辟支佛道、入菩薩位，乃至阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，皆當修學八曼茶羅供養法門。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」佛告師子莊嚴王菩薩摩訶薩言：",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時比丘毘闍耶三皤婆者，豈異人乎？",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今文殊師利菩薩是。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時長者上施者，即我釋迦牟尼佛是。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我從是來經於多劫，修行供養此八法門，具獲如上功德利益；",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "餘有眾生隨能修學，亦皆同獲如我所得。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我行菩薩道來經三阿僧祇劫，修滿六度利益眾生，成等正覺，所有光明威德勢力破魔兵眾。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "斯誰力乎？",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698a29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆由供養八曼茶羅道場功德。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故眾生聞說如上八種法門，無宜不學。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b02_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若以華香燈明，若以飲食幡蓋、衣服音樂，讚歎禮拜發願懺悔，隨其力能皆蒙福祐。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或行六波羅蜜時，修立道場，以諸香水若香塗地，若水若土作方圓壇，斯即名為檀波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "修供養時，身口意業不惱眾生，斯即名為尸波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "修供養時，若有蟲螘來入道場，驅去還來，爾時安忍，斯即名為羼提波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "修供養時，善心相續，斯即名為毘梨耶波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心不散亂一心供養，斯即名為禪波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作業之時，方壇圓場無有偏斜，善能通曉廢立機候，斯即名為般若波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一法隨心變現，即能具足六波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應當廣說教化眾生，為大利益乃至成佛。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」說此經已，師子莊嚴王菩薩摩訶薩，及諸天、龍、夜叉、乾闥婆、阿修羅、迦樓羅、緊那羅、摩睺羅伽、人非人等，皆大歡喜，信受奉行。",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b17_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "師子莊嚴王菩薩請問經",
        "from": "T14n0486_001:0698b18_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]